<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <meta charset='utf-8'>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
    <script src="/javascripts/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        @import url(http://fonts.googleapis.com/earlyaccess/notosanskr.css);
        .title {
            width: 1000px;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR';
            font-size: 18px;
            text-align: left;
            height: 30px;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #4daeb2ff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 18px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR';
            color: #f4f4f4ff;
            width: 100px;
            height: 35px;
        }
        .head {
            background-color: #eeeeeeee;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR';
            font-size: 18px;
            text-align: center;
            width: 200px;
            height: 35px;
        }
        .body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR';
            font-size: 18px;
            text-align: center;
            width: 300px;
            height: 35px;
        }
        table {
            border: 1px solid black;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        td {
            border: 1px solid black;
        }
        .text {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR';
            font-size: 15px;
            text-align: left;
            width: 1000px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div align="center">
        <div class="title">백신 예약 변경</div>
        <table>
            <tr>
                <td class="head" style="width: 50px;">변경</td>
                <td class="head" style="width: 150px;">예약 날짜</td>
                <td class="head" style="width: 100px;">예약 시간</td>
                <td class="head" style="width: 400px;">예약 병원</td>
                <td class="head" style="width: 200px;">예약 백신</td>
                <td class="head" style="width: 100px;">접종 차수</td>
            </tr>

            <%for(var i=0; i < rows0.length; i++){%>
                <tr>
                    <td class="body" style="width: 50px;"><input type="radio" name="change"></td>
                    <td class="body" style="width: 150px;"><%=rows0[i].rdate%></td>
                    <td class="body" style="width: 100px;"><%=rows0[i].rtime%></td>
                    <td class="body" style="width: 400px;"><%=rows2[0].hname%></td>
                    <td class="body" style="width: 200px;"><%=rows0[i].vname%></td>
                    <td class="body" style="width: 100px;"><%=i+1%>차</td>
                </tr>
            <%}%>
        </table><br>
        <div style="height: 10px;"></div>
        <div style="width: 1000px; text-align: center">
            <button class="button" type="button" onclick="location.href='/vaccine/changersv'">다음</button>
        </div>
        <div style="height: 40px"></div>
        <div class="text">
            * 1차 예약 변경 시 2차 예약 정보도 자동으로 변경됩니다.<br>
            * 2차 예약은 변경만 가능하며 1차 접종과 일정 간격 이후 날짜로 변경이 가능합니다.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>